('104113566', 'applestore', 'United States', 'New version error', 'This is a great app which I have been using for many years, but this latest version often pauses playing a song for no reason.  I have premium and have all songs downloaded for offline listening.  For some reason when I\'m driving and listening to my favorite playlist, it just pauses right in the middle of playing, or it won\'t start playing the currently selected song no matter how many times I press play.  The only fix is to track forward or backward one song in the playlist.  I have the latest version of iPhone OS, so I\'m not sure if it\'s that or if it\'s the Spotify software.  Same thing happens on my daughter\'s iPhone when she is riding in the car and has her spotify playing songs.  Has been happening for about a month now.  Hope they fix this bug in the next revision.', '423812891', 'applestore', 'Germany', 'Top', 'Very strong selection + good song quality', 'Spotify', 0.0450573, 0, 0, 1, 1, '2017-03-23 10:16:40', 'all', 9, 1, 1, 1, 'br', 'ot'),
