('105616908', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Value is navigating traffic declined', 'I first downloaded and used Waze to navigate around traffic. When traffic would start to build, it was helpful to have it find alternative routes that saved a few minutes. In the last 3-6 months, that feature seems to broken. All the route adjustments say they are saving time, but actually add minutes to the estimated arrival time. Also, Waze has not been navigating away from traffic recently, but putting me right into the thick of it. The estimates on how long it\'ll take to get through the traffic are completely off. This app needs a revamp.', '8518416', 'applestore', 'Germany', 'Good scout', 'Quickly find good replacement routes for clogged roads', 'Waze', 0.034047, 1, 0, 1, 1, '2017-03-23 10:19:07', 'all', 12, 0, 1, 0.875, 'br', 'ot'),
