('285651696', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Used to have premium, never again', 'I had premium, and enjoyed it. It seemed worthwhile unlimited music $10 a month; same as a few other choices. Nothing really special about spotify.\n\nI\'m pretty broke, been so for a while. Cancel spotify. Hadn\'t used it much since I stopped paying for it, most of my use was from my phone. I started using it again recently, since I\'ve been on wifi for long enough periods of time to make installing and using it worthwhile. There are a lot of ads. That alone wouldn\'t usually bother me too much, I understand they have to make money. But I\'ve sat through up to 4 ads in a row, changed a track, and got another add. Usually they\'re 30 seconds long.\n\nAgain just ads wouldn\'t bother me, but they\'re all for spotify pro. So I guess they\'re trying to annoy me into spending my money? Dang, I mean I figured they\'d make more money with advertisers. Anyway, I\'ll never pay for it spotify again. Apple music never tried to annoy me into re-subscribing and netflix lets me freeze my account.', '165203642', 'applestore', 'Germany', '...', 'Use the app almost 1 year with premium. I\'ve always been very happy with it, but for about 1-2 months, already loaded songs are hanging up and you can neither rewind nor back! Nerves very strong momentarily !!', 'Spotify', 0.0985239, 1, 0, 1, 1, '2017-03-24 13:36:40', 'all', 144, 0, 3, 0.625, 'ot', 'ot'),
('286753493', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Completely stopped working', 'I don\'t know what\'s going on but my spotify is acting up. I try shuffle a playlist or play top fifty IT changes songs and doesn\'t play anything. Half the songs are unavailable I don\'t know why and when I click on a playlist it shows that there is nothing on it and to browse for songs when there are at least 20 songs on it. I don\'t know what to do and I love this app and I\'ve tried everything in settings thinking that it had something to do with my location or something but nothing changed in my settings or anything and it\'s something wrong with the app. I love this app so much and I use it frequently so would you mind fixing it please? Thanks', '100572037', 'applestore', 'Germany', 'Playlists Logic is missing from the developers!', 'So I have Spotify actually only because it is not charged on the data volume of the Telekom, otherwise I would not spend a cent on it ... I mean, how can one expect that I have to select every song in my Playlist to delete? How can one expect that I have to click each song individually and then insert into a play list and not as in Apple 2/3 or all select and can add or delete them at a stroke? So I look at it for years and shake for years with the head ... I need an hour until I created a Playlist, which takes Apple 10 seconds! Please dear Spotify Team! Wrote to me that you finally implement times and I will delete my rating! ???  Thank you in advance! And since glad that I wrote this here ... I think I would have had to wait another 2 years, until her times by itself drauf comes that you can copy synonymous times from Apple and not just vice versa ... But I mean mine ... these are Basics ?????????????', 'Spotify', 0.215404, 1, 1, 1, 1, '2017-03-24 13:38:21', 'all', 145, 1, 1, 1, 'br', 'ot'),
