('404630248', 'applestore', 'United States', 'I Love WAZE', 'The best real time traffic app out there!', '148377330', 'applestore', 'Germany', 'Hammer', 'That is exactly what I was looking for: a navi that brings me fastest way through the major city traffic jam. Through the smallest streets, if necessary via parking lots. I am surprised to find out which way is the best today. I know myself really well, but Waze always finds surprising ways and trick 17 and 18. Also on routine stretches I do not go without without, the adjustment of the route and the warnings come in real time. Fortunately, traffic jams are also recorded in the smallest streets. Bad luck is when no Wazer was on the road. Absolutely this lovingly designed and daily delight-making app use. Since we have everything from. Waze is definitely the most useful, funniest, most playful and best working app on my iPhone. There are even more features, since no wishes remain open. Only you have to give yourself. Thanks to the developers!', 'Waze', 0.208607, 1, 1, 1, 1, '2017-03-24 15:23:58', 'all', 226, 2, 2, 1, 'ot', 'ot'),
