('536084969', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Mediocre', 'Waze doesn\'t provide an ability to turn on location services to only when the app is in use.  Even Google Maps allows this battery saving and privacy enhancing feature.  Also, I don\'t understand why I need a warning for cars parked on the shoulder, as that\'s not a serious safety hazard in my mind.  Finally, the maps are so cartoonish and crudely drawn that they are hard to follow in areas with multiple offramps and intersections.  \n\nThe one plus of Waze is the crowd sourced information for real road hazards and speed traps.  Given how little value add the rest of the app is, I\'m surprised Google hasn\'t just shut down Waze and integrated the information into Maps.', '191103106', 'applestore', 'Germany', 'Please show the list of events again and report traffic jams !!!!', 'It used to be better ... a shame!\r\n\r\nPlease re-enter the message list for congestion, accidents and other handicaps in the vicinity !!!\r\n\r\nIn addition, reporting traffic jams and other events on the counter-track!\r\n\r\nAlso larger symbols of the\r\nEvents that do not disappear almost completely during zooming on larger map sections and are thus hardly readable!\r\n\r\nIn addition, current traffic reports of the police and other providers are missing ... why?\r\n\r\nTherefore only three instead of five stars! This is when the event list and the message button for the other side are displayed!\r\n\r\nOtherwise, I informed myself before the start of the announcements in my vicinity ... Please again the introduction and these important messages indicate. Also, reporting congestion and disability on the counter-track is there no longer? Why? Could this report easily and inform other drivers if there is traffic jam!\r\n\r\nPlease reintroduce these two important functions, then there are five stars! Otherwise great app!\r\n\r\nAnother wish: My idea: in the case of traffic reports such as construction sites, danger areas and accidents, the Wazer should be able to report how long this event occurs, as is the case with closures. Accidents reported by Wazern would have to be longer or shorter in the system, depending on the severity. Also construction sites, as these are sometimes either day-care sites or long-term. And thus different long as a message should emerge. Otherwise, the app works great! And getting better and better! Everyone should try it out and join in, so that the roads become safer and faster and safer! And best informed is where it is on the streets and where free travel is! Thumbs up!!! Continue so and join in! Continue to make love developers !!! Thank you very much!!!', 'Waze', 0.219768, 1, 1, 1, 1, '2017-03-25 22:32:54', 'all', 313, 0, 0, 1, 'ot', 'ot'),
