('101090693', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Crashes & risky reporting', 'I\'ve used Waze for several years now and it\'s always improving. It\'s one of my frequent \"go to\" GPS\'s, and has a lot of good features. I especially like that I can pre-plan trips and that it picks up scheduled trips from my calendar. It may be just my phone, but I often have this app crash while using it though. And what I don\'t like is it\'s a BIG distraction to report road issues or even just give a thumbs up to a fellow Wazer for reporting something. It really doesn\'t make sense to me that we should report road issues WHILE DRIVING. It\'s certainly helpful to other Wazers, that\'s a given, but it\'s no different than the distraction of illegal texting to me. There\'s many times I\'ve wanted to report problems on the road, but to do it I\'d have to take my attention off the road, and even seconds could be too long as texting while driving has proven. Maybe the future of Waze could incorporate a means to give a verbal report to fellow Wazers. Just saying...', '159117742', 'applestore', 'Germany', 'Mobile Blitzer', 'I\'ve been using the app for some time. The navigation is basically good. The timely reminder of going to appointments in calendar with addresses super. But there are two things that disturb me: 1) I am / has never been warned before mobile flashers. Have so often on my route this had, also report them themselves (there are no Waze points?), But I have never been warned. Either does not work or the people in my region Ludwigshafen / Palatinate report nothing. 2) If I drive but differently as the Navi it ​​wants (note: iPhone is also connected with Autoradio due to electricity and music), then a short telephone connection is established to myself, during which the music or Radiowiedergabe for about 4 seconds interrupted becomes. It\'s frustrating.', 'Waze', 0.200168, 1, 1, 1, 1, '2017-03-25 22:59:22', 'long', 352, 1, 0, 0.875, 'ot', 'br'),
('101373291', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Overalll good app', 'There needs to be some improvement. I only use the app because it lets me know where cops, and hazards are. If it wasn\'t for that, I wouldn\'t bother. It\'s a bit annoying all the \"alerts for\nCars on the shoulder of the road\", I wish it could give a different alert. Also a lot of Street names are incorrect and it doesn\'t ask you if you want to take a quicker route and the difference in time... it\'s just starts redirecting you.... I don\'t like that feature, it\'s a little confusing.', '191103106', 'applestore', 'Germany', 'Please show the list of events again and report traffic jams !!!!', 'It used to be better ... a shame!\r\n\r\nPlease re-enter the message list for congestion, accidents and other handicaps in the vicinity !!!\r\n\r\nIn addition, reporting traffic jams and other events on the counter-track!\r\n\r\nAlso larger symbols of the\r\nEvents that do not disappear almost completely during zooming on larger map sections and are thus hardly readable!\r\n\r\nIn addition, current traffic reports of the police and other providers are missing ... why?\r\n\r\nTherefore only three instead of five stars! This is when the event list and the message button for the other side are displayed!\r\n\r\nOtherwise, I informed myself before the start of the announcements in my vicinity ... Please again the introduction and these important messages indicate. Also, reporting congestion and disability on the counter-track is there no longer? Why? Could this report easily and inform other drivers if there is traffic jam!\r\n\r\nPlease reintroduce these two important functions, then there are five stars! Otherwise great app!\r\n\r\nAnother wish: My idea: in the case of traffic reports such as construction sites, danger areas and accidents, the Wazer should be able to report how long this event occurs, as is the case with closures. Accidents reported by Wazern would have to be longer or shorter in the system, depending on the severity. Also construction sites, as these are sometimes either day-care sites or long-term. And thus different long as a message should emerge. Otherwise, the app works great! And getting better and better! Everyone should try it out and join in, so that the roads become safer and faster and safer! And best informed is where it is on the streets and where free travel is! Thumbs up!!! Continue so and join in! Continue to make love developers !!! Thank you very much!!!', 'Waze', 0.200366, 1, 1, 1, 1, '2017-03-25 23:01:48', 'long', 353, -1, 0, 0.875, 'ot', 'ot'),
('101776350', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Recommend Waze', 'If you have to travel long distances, I recommend using this app. The app will notify you of traffic jams ahead allowing you to avoid the traffic. I like that you can see pictures of your destination. Thank you Waze!', '155212219', 'applestore', 'Germany', 'No traffic jam!', 'Thanks Waze I\'ve already been able to avoid some traffic jams. Thank you!', 'Waze', 0.329008, 2, 2, 1, 1, '2017-03-25 23:03:19', 'long', 354, 1, 1, 1, 'ot', 'br'),
('102321976', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Good gps app,', 'Can be more useful if when you zoom in street names were to show.', '8518416', 'applestore', 'Germany', 'Good scout', 'Quickly find good replacement routes for clogged roads', 'Waze', 0.0639285, 1, 0, 1, 1, '2017-03-25 23:03:54', 'long', 355, 1, 1, 1, 'fr', 'ot'),
('102537963', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Battery Drain', 'This app is a battery killer! Great app, but please change the options of GPS usage. This app should have the option of tracking \"When in use\", that will save time and the hassle of turning the access on and off. Although it may benefits the developers, there is NO WAY I\'m letting this app track my every move with an \"Always\" setting. Nope! Thanks for the ride and off you go!', '148377330', 'applestore', 'Germany', 'Hammer', 'That is exactly what I was looking for: a navi that brings me fastest way through the major city traffic jam. Through the smallest streets, if necessary via parking lots. I am surprised to find out which way is the best today. I know myself really well, but Waze always finds surprising ways and trick 17 and 18. Also on routine stretches I do not go without without, the adjustment of the route and the warnings come in real time. Fortunately, traffic jams are also recorded in the smallest streets. Bad luck is when no Wazer was on the road. Absolutely this lovingly designed and daily delight-making app use. Since we have everything from. Waze is definitely the most useful, funniest, most playful and best working app on my iPhone. There are even more features, since no wishes remain open. Only you have to give yourself. Thanks to the developers!', 'Waze', 0.212817, 1, 0, 1, 1, '2017-03-25 23:04:56', 'long', 356, 0, 2, 0.75, 'ot', 'ot'),
('10264360', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Great app', 'This is a great app especially for when there is traffic. It always find the best shortcut', '127668819', 'applestore', 'Germany', 'Not always the shortest routes ...', 'But for umme, it is still a great app', 'Waze', 0.234157, 1, 2, 1, 1, '2017-03-25 23:06:54', 'long', 357, 2, 2, 1, 'ot', 'ot'),
('104709849', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Disappointing', 'If this app & the support team worked properly maybe it\'d be better than Apple Music. The app has tons of glitches regardless of the updates, I have tried contacting the support team to help me out and I never heard back. Sudden shut-downs happen far too often despite he app being removed and reinstalled. Just changing the email address on the account is difficult enough.', '4107383', 'applestore', 'Germany', 'class', 'Really good, and usable on many devices', 'Spotify', 0.0274368, 0, 0, 1, 1, '2017-03-25 23:07:18', 'long', 358, 0, 2, 0.75, 'ot', 'ot'),
('106069357', 'applestore', 'United States', 'My go to GPS', 'Thank you for a great app! I recommend it to everyone. I use this app daily, even just to find out the quickest route to where I\'m going. It\'s saved me from being stuck in traffic, quickly re-routed me, and helped me avoid being late for work so many times. Love it!', '197653522', 'applestore', 'Germany', 'Super App - I am thrilled', 'I love the app. It is easy to use and has always brought me safely to my goal. Great, I also find the opportunity to set an arrival time and Waze tells me then when I should go! ??????', 'Waze', 0.202085, 2, 1, 1, 1, '2017-03-25 23:07:52', 'long', 359, 2, 3, 0.875, 'ot', 'ot'),
