('108055571', 'applestore', 'United States', 'No way', 'Waze has been a good app until the recent update but in the past few months it become more intrusive and a road safety hazard. The app is nosy as it now wants to access the contact list, pops up more in your face ads, and wants to run in the background to track your movement. Compromising the driving experience with intrusive ads is a total no. Tracking me after I arrived at the destination is also not this app business. This is a GPS app and not a social network gateway app. For this reason I regret upgrading this app. Nothing good lasts forever.', '8518416', 'applestore', 'Germany', 'Good scout', 'Quickly find good replacement routes for clogged roads', 'Waze', 0.0458872, 0, 0, 1, 1, '2017-03-25 23:12:52', 'long', 362, 0, 1, 0.875, 'ot', 'ot'),
