('160085016', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Backward and Directionless', 'Waze is good for some routine trips but the short cuts leave a lot to be desired, if I didn\'t have my own sense of direction I would have been lost many times. Just last week Waze sent me South on 270 when the north bound option was available. I would not rely on Waze if you don\'t know the area.', '8518416', 'applestore', 'Germany', 'Good scout', 'Quickly find good replacement routes for clogged roads', 'Waze', 0.0358695, 1, 0, 1, 1, '2017-03-26 00:51:57', 'long', 409, 1, 1, 1, 'ot', 'ot'),
