('190264868', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Great app till the finish flag and some specific geographical areas', 'I work as an in home caregiver. This app has lead me to many homes in an efficient manner. But when I get to the street, it shows the \"title\" from the calendar. I need the house number. I have to pull over and switch back to the calendar to see the house number.\n\nSomeone has not inputted the house numbers along the Access Roads in Clyde, TX. So, I cannot find client\'s homes. \n\nMap editors in the Abilene TX area do not want to drive the routes to see what issues I am reporting. Took three months before it told me to use a marked on ramp instead of traveling to the next on ramp. \n\nI have had better response in the other areas I have traveled.', '144419433', 'applestore', 'Germany', 'For the house use it is enough', 'Completely out.', 'Waze', 0.216616, 0, 0, 1, 1, '2017-03-26 13:20:38', 'long', 430, 0, 0, 1, 'ot', 'ot'),
