('19821149', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Better than  others', 'I love this app. In over a year of constant use, it has yet to lead me the wrong way, as some of the other apps, and my own dedicated GPS has done. As with any GPS, one has to use some common sense, pay attention to the road, and realize that technology is not perfect. Mistakes happen. I love the interactive hazard notification. It allows users to give real time ground truth about accidents, road work, stalled vehicles, police,and many more. I like knowing my other friends are using the app as well. Best of GPS and social media being melded in one app. Use it. Just makes the app and us stronger as a traveling community.', '191103106', 'applestore', 'Germany', 'Please show the list of events again and report traffic jams !!!!', 'It used to be better ... a shame!\r\n\r\nPlease re-enter the message list for congestion, accidents and other handicaps in the vicinity !!!\r\n\r\nIn addition, reporting traffic jams and other events on the counter-track!\r\n\r\nAlso larger symbols of the\r\nEvents that do not disappear almost completely during zooming on larger map sections and are thus hardly readable!\r\n\r\nIn addition, current traffic reports of the police and other providers are missing ... why?\r\n\r\nTherefore only three instead of five stars! This is when the event list and the message button for the other side are displayed!\r\n\r\nOtherwise, I informed myself before the start of the announcements in my vicinity ... Please again the introduction and these important messages indicate. Also, reporting congestion and disability on the counter-track is there no longer? Why? Could this report easily and inform other drivers if there is traffic jam!\r\n\r\nPlease reintroduce these two important functions, then there are five stars! Otherwise great app!\r\n\r\nAnother wish: My idea: in the case of traffic reports such as construction sites, danger areas and accidents, the Wazer should be able to report how long this event occurs, as is the case with closures. Accidents reported by Wazern would have to be longer or shorter in the system, depending on the severity. Also construction sites, as these are sometimes either day-care sites or long-term. And thus different long as a message should emerge. Otherwise, the app works great! And getting better and better! Everyone should try it out and join in, so that the roads become safer and faster and safer! And best informed is where it is on the streets and where free travel is! Thumbs up!!! Continue so and join in! Continue to make love developers !!! Thank you very much!!!', 'Waze', 0.220803, 1, 1, 1, 1, '2017-03-26 13:23:51', 'long', 436, 1, 0, 0.875, 'ot', 'ot'),
