('256430849', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Dangerous & dubious', 'Waze frequently directs me through heavier traffic than necessary, likes to have me take dangerous left hand turns through fast, unrelenting traffic and expects that I can, say, turn right onto a 5,6 lane major road and cut through 3 lanes in 600,700 feet to turn left when that\'s just not possible. In short, Waze defies logic and has been both nerve wracking and slightly dangerous. Not at all recommended.', '11100433', 'applestore', 'Germany', 'Very good app, but lives from the participation', 'Use Waze now for over 4 years always whenever I go. Navigation is better than the built-in navi. Would be good if all users would do so. Overall, Waze gets better with every version.', 'Waze', 0.042287, 0, 0, 1, 1, '2017-03-26 14:22:07', 'long', 477, 1, 2, 0.875, 'ot', 'ot'),
('256546268', 'applestore', 'United States', 'App has gone bad', 'As a long time user of Spotify, I can easily say that Spotify has been doing horrible lately. Not only does it not play certain songs you want in a playlist (make a playlist with one song in it, play it, and it plays another random song {???}) it also plays ads after every, no joke, every song. I can\'t listen through two whole songs without \"listen to this add for 30 minutes of add free music!\" (Then app crashes/ plays 5 ads in a row/ etc.) Not to mention Spotify Premium is $12+?!? Definitely not worth it when you can go on a computer and do the same thing you could do with premium, but free. Spotify used to be a spectacular app but now I\'m very VERY disappointed. I just deleted the app and is going back to Pandora. Don\'t waste your time with this app.', '129703454', 'applestore', 'Germany', '2 bugs and 2 wishes. Otherwise top.', 'I am very pleased. Only there is a bug that tells me I would be offline and will prevent me from listening to a podcast (fixed and fluffy) even though I had downloaded it before. Also, I would like if I could determine what melm start screen is in the app. I always hear my playlists and do not want to always have to go there. The function and song pure to hear in which one long drauf tippt is with me also buggy. Does not often fold. Lyrics would be nice.', 'Spotify', 0.206511, 1, 0, 1, 1, '2017-03-26 14:24:43', 'long', 478, -2, 1, 0.625, 'ot', 'ot'),
