('261916808', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Only I rate performance superstars like this one or fails', 'Still a very good and has saved me time money and gas. The basic gps has gotten more jittery and the app features however have gotten more intrusive especially in the middle of recalculations and has covered up changes were the best route  It has gotten more tricky to identify issues in the opposite lane but it is still good for working with all of your fellow vehicle occupants.  It saves time and money.  It works well on the train. While it has given me a few extra turns especially at the beginning of the trip, it is a must for active construction areas areas with revenue traffic cameras and trips during seasonal congestion like college move in days. I rated it very highly before but dropped 2 stars', '191103106', 'applestore', 'Germany', 'Please show the list of events again and report traffic jams !!!!', 'It used to be better ... a shame!\r\n\r\nPlease re-enter the message list for congestion, accidents and other handicaps in the vicinity !!!\r\n\r\nIn addition, reporting traffic jams and other events on the counter-track!\r\n\r\nAlso larger symbols of the\r\nEvents that do not disappear almost completely during zooming on larger map sections and are thus hardly readable!\r\n\r\nIn addition, current traffic reports of the police and other providers are missing ... why?\r\n\r\nTherefore only three instead of five stars! This is when the event list and the message button for the other side are displayed!\r\n\r\nOtherwise, I informed myself before the start of the announcements in my vicinity ... Please again the introduction and these important messages indicate. Also, reporting congestion and disability on the counter-track is there no longer? Why? Could this report easily and inform other drivers if there is traffic jam!\r\n\r\nPlease reintroduce these two important functions, then there are five stars! Otherwise great app!\r\n\r\nAnother wish: My idea: in t