('321598414', 'applestore', 'United States', 'What happened?', 'For some reason, these past 6 months the app has gotten worse and worse. The directions don\'t reroute you due to traffic anymore, or give you the option to avoid it. Seems like every time I\'m on a 2 hour drive it turns out to be 4 hours. \nThe network drops all of the time and the alerts don\'t give you the correct distance/time to get over a lane to exit. \nThe app used to update you with alerts and available changes... it doesn\'t anymore. \nPlease fix this issues.', '8518416', 'applestore', 'Germany', 'Good scout', 'Quickly find good replacement routes for clogged roads', 'Waze', 0.00657336, 0, 0, 1, 1, '2017-03-26 15:09:50', 'long', 517, -1, 1, 0.75, 'br', 'ot'),
